---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portfolio — Zack Jean">
  <main>
    <h1>Portfolio</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A selection of automation systems, tooling, and AI programs I've built.</p>

    <div class="work-grid">

      <a href="/work/scorecard" class="card featured">
        <span class="badge">Featured</span>
        <h2>Technical Support Specialist Scorecard</h2>
        <p>Automated QA scoring system integrating ticketing, Toggl time-tracking, SLA metrics, and escalation data via APIs into a unified analyst dashboard.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>Python</span><span>REST APIs</span><span>Zoho Desk</span><span>Toggl</span><span>Google Sheets</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/toggl-sheets" class="card">
        <h2>Toggl → Sheets Automation</h2>
        <p>Apps Script pipeline pulling multi-workspace Toggl data into Google Sheets with daily triggers, billable filters, and automated monthly exports.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>Apps Script</span><span>Toggl API</span><span>Google Sheets</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/ops-revenue" class="card">
        <h2>Ops Revenue Report</h2>
        <p>Automated Gmail report with inline HTML styling, data pipeline from ops systems, and row-capping logic to stay within email size limits.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>Apps Script</span><span>Gmail API</span><span>Monday.com</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/ai-enablement" class="card">
        <h2>Claude AI Enablement Program</h2>
        <p>Three-session education roadmap rolling out Claude adoption org-wide, including training materials, prompt libraries, and usage tracking.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>Claude</span><span>AI Strategy</span><span>L&D</span><span>Prompt Engineering</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/monday-board" class="card">
        <h2>Monday.com Board Manager</h2>
        <p>Apps Script integration with declarative field config, parallel batch fetching, and GraphQL API calls for real-time ops dashboards.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>JavaScript</span><span>Monday.com</span><span>GraphQL</span><span>Apps Script</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/make-sop" class="card">
        <h2>Make.com Automation SOP</h2>
        <p>Enterprise-grade SOP covering governance, security, architecture, logging, and deployment standards across a multi-team automation platform.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>Make.com</span><span>Documentation</span><span>Ops</span><span>Automation</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-muted, #888);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .work-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e5e5e5);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent, #555);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .card.featured {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    background: var(--color-accent, #111);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .card h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-muted, #666);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tags span {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-tag-bg, #f0f0f0);
    color: var(--color-tag-text, #444);
    padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
</style>